{"tid":626853,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Shake Shack香港限定店","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T16:40:48.000Z","uid":120258,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"535db6b51075d04ca8d3667fa385057144d9d065","tid":626853,"uid":120258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"在 2 月份時，Shake Shack 已預告香港首家分店即將開幕，而門店正式開業之前，這家美國人氣連鎖漢堡店更宣布將在國際金融中心商場開設一日 Pop-Up 期間限定店以作預熱。據悉，4 月 14 日上午 11 時至下午 4 時期間，ifc 一樓中庭將搖身一變成綠草如茵的公園，重現紐約麥迪遜廣場公園的輕快活力氛圍。前往 Pop-Up 的顧客可率先試食如 ShackBurger、&lsquo;Shroom Burger 及 Crinkle-Cut Fries 等 Shake Shack 的主打美食，同時該期間限定店更將設置充滿紐約及香港文化特色裝飾的 Shake Shack 巨型棋盤，在香港的 Shake Shack 迷們可不要錯過了！<br />\n<br />\nShake Shack 香港一日 Pop-Up<br />\n地點：香港中環金融街 8 號國際金融中心商場一樓中庭<br />\n時間：2018 年 4 月 14 日（星期六）早上 11 時至下午 4 時<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/4/shake-shack-hong-kong-ifc-pop-up?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F4%2Fshake-shack-hong-kong-ifc-pop-up%3Famp%3D1&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=19f6d047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/4/shake-shack-hong-kong-ifc-pop-up?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ndllm到時班死港女又有新打卡熱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56c21844a3720d2b120e4eda4240818bb4c8a6d","tid":626853,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"去外國食算  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaf4b787ff2ef479b333621072945abe6e3871f","tid":626853,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係同金拱門一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945ccf5ae6303